channel.title: My development Thread-Penguinscape pkz v.5(Might be the final one)*pics*
channel.description:
Hey moparscape,it's me rs w00dcut as you all know.I have a server called Penguinscape pkz.I've been recently reading up on java and been searching for great tuts that help me learn/Get smarter in java knowledge as in everyday Life.Below are a list of accomplishmens/Pictures/Info That I have done so far for Penguinscape pkz v.5 Note:This really might be the last version,I'm running out of ideas.So PM me your ideas etc. Below are some things My server has already in it:
[ul][li]Agility training+ In wild course[/li] [li]Full fletching and flax spinning.[/li][/ul]
[ul][li]Full smithing,Bronze-Rune[/li] [li]it's now edgeville based[/li][/ul]
[ul][li]You can now use Ice barrage-Fixed that[/li] [li]Added Abyss for RuneCrafting[/li][/ul]
[ul][li]Added A glory-Takes you to agility course[/li] [li]Added cooking[/li][/ul]
Things I wish to add to server:
[ul][li]Farming[/li] [li]Woodcutting-All trees and axes[/li][/ul]
[ul][li]FireMaking[/li] [li]Maybe leather/D-Hide Crafting.[/li][/ul]
**No it's not silabs,I just used her client to see in game item Id's** [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img223.imageshack.us/img223/4421/fullcookingiv7.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img405.imageshack.us/img405/5521/workingicebarragevn6.png[/img][/URL]
[b]Suggestions-We need your HELP![/b] [b]PM THIS TO ME ONLY!![/b] [code]Suggestion Name- Link for me to add that into my server- Purpose- Why should I add this- Msn(For further Info on the Suggestion)-[/code]
